\b Simmer
\b0 \'a0the lemon and water in a large pot until the peels are tender.\'a0 A good test is to try to cut them with a wooden or plastic spoon:\'a0 if they break apart effortlessly, it\'92s done.\'a0 This takes me about 20-25 minutes.\
